name: Ghost of a Building
description: All that you're seeing here doesn't exist anymore. In 2014, at the moment the photo was taken, this building was a Carrefour supermarket. It was rebuilt from the ground up in 2018. This work is part of a series named "Worthless Gurskys". Coordinates: -23.570152, -46.661983. Originally released on 10 May 2021 as HeN OBJKT 73118.
